item.title: CVE-2015-9132|2024-09-17T01:56:27.859Z -- qualcomm%2C%20inc. -- snapdragon%20mobile%2Csmall%20cell%20soc
item.description: In Android before 2018-04-05 or earlier security patch level on Qualcomm Snapdragon Mobile and Small Cell SoC FSM9055, SD 210/SD 212/SD 205, SD 400, SD 410/12, SD 615/16/SD 415, SD 800, and SD 810, possible arbitrary memory read due to untrusted pointer dereference when handling HLOS controlled values passed to the QSEE syscall helper.
